reviewText: This is one of the best performances in the music industry period!  The acoustics and the lyrics blow away any individual who listens to their music. Many new comers to La Ley (including myself) do not expect much of them, but from the moment the guitars, the drums, and the lyrics are mixed together, you begin to zone out, an effect only the greatest music can produce.  Some music takes a while to get into, but finally you love it; other you love from the gecko.  You will feel the music running through your spine from the first time you hear it.  For years many of us have been waiting for the DVD version to be released, and finally here it is. Enough said!
summary: The oracle of rock en español

reviewText: I wasn't a La Ley fan until I heard this CD.  Everysong is awesome.  These unplugged versions of the original songs are even better than the originals.  I've seen them a couple of times in concert perfoming these song and they're even better live.  This is a must have dvd.

reviewText: There's no doubt that 2001 was their year. They won a Grammy award and performend this excellent show with Mtv.On this DVD you can see the whole show without cuts. The production it's purely first class, from the song selection and the duet with Ely Guerra on "El duelo". You can find one song in English and another in French besides their hits in Spanish. The sound is very good, the chours are also great. Everything is very good. As a matter of fact this is one of the best Mtv Unpluggeds ever in the Latin category.Besides the show you can find lyrics in english and other special features.
summary: The best work yet of La Ley.

reviewText: I saw this concert on TV and ever since I have been waiting for it to come out of in DVD, La ley gives a magnificent performance and also Elly Guerra who joins them in a duo for " El Duelo " it is outstanding. This is a must have on DVD concert for people who like La Ley dont miss out of this DVD when ever it comes out 2 thumbs up!!!!

reviewText: Finally, the remarkable MTV unplugged of La Ley is released in DVD format! This is something all the fans have been waiting since 2001, when the show was first aired! La Ley is the best rock band of Latin America. Their MTV unplugged is great and I often listen to the CD. Even if you are not a fan of this band or dont't know any of their songs, check out the DVD and also the unplugged CD. "Fuera de mi" is my favorite song in this unplugged MTV, because Beto Cuevas gives a great interpretation, which is really touching. I also like "mentira", el duelo" and "aqui". Buy now'. You don't have to wait anymore for this DVD!
summary: La Ley is the best rock group of Latin America!
